Allez-y ! Encerclez-moi ces pirates !

00:19:54.580 --> 00:19:57.250
Tayaut !

00:19:58.330 --> 00:19:59.170
- La Marine ! - Tss...

00:20:05.750 --> 00:20:06.470
Trop fort !

